<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2ead4); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#b98229; margin-bottom:1rem;">Local Expertise</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:400; font-variation-settings:'opsz' 32; line-height:1.2; color:#191817; margin-bottom:1.75rem;">Modern executive estates with bayside reach.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Wakerley is one of the eastern corridor's most consistent modern family suburbs, defined by larger executive homes, quiet residential streets and a layout that has matured into a settled, low-density address. It attracts upgraders from across the inner east, returning expats, and interstate family buyers comparing Brisbane's bayside against Sydney's south and Melbourne's east, drawn by block size, lifestyle and the easy reach to both the CBD and Moreton Bay.
    </p>
